{"id": 1193, "genre": 1001, "title": "城市生活中，你遇到过哪些“小确麻烦”？", "description": "一些不至于让你觉得“我要搬家”，但又经常会发生的困扰。（题图来自：Christoph Frei）", "record_count": 3695, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160830144736r6Bq4PfQcdD7jRV2.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-31T03:00:13Z", "options": [{"id": 199957, "content": "我早饭该吃点啥好？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 837314}, {"id": 120341, "content": "没谈过恋爱，不知道自己是不是喜欢上了一个人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 768994}, {"id": 111900, "content": "UBER滴滴遇到不熟路的司机", "image": null, "praise_count": 260, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 318224}, {"id": 111901, "content": "感觉很多地方都长得一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 83, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722484}, {"id": 111902, "content": "今天中午吃啥？", "image": null, "praise_count": 346, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 666428}, {"id": 111903, "content": "堵车，但没堵死。", "image": null, "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 111904, "content": "离地铁一公里，走路有点远，等公交也不合适，自行车怕丢", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 573384}, {"id": 111905, "content": "周围不是服务老人就是服务小孩的餐馆、小店、娱乐设施，中、青、少感觉被社会抛弃，说好的主力消费人群在此地区完全失效。", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493}, {"id": 111906, "content": "地铁在早晚高峰的时候人特别多但是挤挤总可以挤进去，可真的挤进去了又有点后悔?", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 208253}, {"id": 111907, "content": "一日三餐...", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739812}, {"id": 111908, "content": "回家要爬9楼", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 193260}, {"id": 111909, "content": "每天来回爬九楼，经常下班回家后，再也不想下来", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737911}, {"id": 113445, "content": "短距离出行坐公交车怕堵车，但是地铁安检越来越麻烦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747023}, {"id": 111910, "content": "一个人就是最大的麻烦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736737}, {"id": 111911, "content": "约炮遇到前任", "image": null, "praise_count": 74, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739959}, {"id": 111912, "content": "隔壁一装修简直想炸楼", "image": null, "praise_count": 77, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 701648}, {"id": 111913, "content": "总丢公交卡", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 707716}, {"id": 111914, "content": "G hochi igugxigxgxiigcohchcvuycoycugogxcfyooyxoch", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709110}, {"id": 111915, "content": "城市太大，城市太小，装不下一个人，装下了千千万万的人\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709110}, {"id": 111916, "content": "家里发现蟑螂。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 728846}, {"id": 111917, "content": "晚饭到底吃不吃？", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738349}, {"id": 111918, "content": "网络不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709777}, {"id": 111920, "content": "永远不知道佛公交车几点能来", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642493}, {"id": 111921, "content": "吃什么是世纪难题", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642493}, {"id": 111922, "content": "家里附近环境不错，就是离公司太远……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739997}, {"id": 111923, "content": "出门没带手机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735250}, {"id": 111924, "content": "6点下班，回家堵个车就快8点了。晚饭呢……", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340881}, {"id": 111925, "content": "附近外卖比较少，自己做饭菜市场嫌脏超市又太远", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 720958}, {"id": 111926, "content": "一个买不起房的上海户口", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740019}, {"id": 111927, "content": "请熟人吃饭，在点完菜发现人家又叫了不认识的人一起，接着就是你吃，他们聊，过后还是你买单", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 379908}, {"id": 111928, "content": "想着要带的东西，睡一觉或者一出门就忘了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726147}, {"id": 111929, "content": "地铁人山人海", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 737191}, {"id": 111930, "content": "隔音不好，邻居又是一对小情侣…", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735120}, {"id": 111931, "content": "每次回家在小区里就要走好远?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 735808}, {"id": 111932, "content": "如何减肚子", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 739153}, {"id": 111934, "content": "楼下坐着一帮大妈天天看你进进出出，每天纠结要不要打招呼", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599058}, {"id": 112190, "content": "总担心小区没车位，都不愿意开出来了。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 80764}, {"id": 111935, "content": "开销大，一睁眼就得花钱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738675}, {"id": 114239, "content": "小区里到处是托管，大中午扰民", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 751211}, {"id": 111936, "content": "家门口最近的商店需要走路10分钟以上，装修公司把装修垃圾随便", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 684069}, {"id": 111938, "content": "上班拥堵，地铁塞车", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277107}, {"id": 112962, "content": "堵车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657468}, {"id": 111939, "content": "666", "image": "img/option/option/20160831124948CM8UxoDYOhqSrZey.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740060}, {"id": 111940, "content": "约个人，你有时间的时候他没时间，他有时间的时你没时间。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 740056}, {"id": 111941, "content": "找不到志同道和的人，什么都不想玩，提不起劲", "image": "img/option/option/20160831125329TmRrLh4P3kuUisa8", "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 264505}, {"id": 111942, "content": "夏天晚上不敢开窗户，全是烧烤味", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 736909}, {"id": 111943, "content": "附近有人装修", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705651}, {"id": 111944, "content": "超市不在楼下 不去了 网购", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 611598}, {"id": 182601, "content": "非要在下楼的过程中抽烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978742}, {"id": 111946, "content": "孤独？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464524}]}